## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="43542-103">Il <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser> controllo offre le funzionalità seguenti:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="43542-103">The <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser> control provides the following capabilities:</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="43542-104">**Navigazione**: <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Source%2A>, <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Navigate%2A>, <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.NavigateToStream%2A>, <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.NavigateToString%2A>e <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Refresh%2A>.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="43542-104">**Navigation**: <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Source%2A>, <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Navigate%2A>, <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.NavigateToStream%2A>, <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.NavigateToString%2A>, and <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Refresh%2A>.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="43542-105">**La durata dello spostamento**: <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Navigating>, <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Navigated>, e <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.LoadCompleted>.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="43542-105">**Navigation Lifetime**: <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Navigating>, <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Navigated>, and <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.LoadCompleted>.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="43542-106">**Inserimento nel diario di navigazione**: <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.CanGoBack%2A>, <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.GoBack%2A>, <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.CanGoForward%2A>, e <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.GoForward%2A>.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="43542-106">**Navigation Journaling**: <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.CanGoBack%2A>, <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.GoBack%2A>, <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.CanGoForward%2A>, and <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.GoForward%2A>.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="43542-107">**Interoperabilità WPF/HTML**: <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.InvokeScript%2A> e <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.ObjectForScripting%2A>, e <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Document%2A>.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="43542-107">**WPF/HTML Interoperability**: <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.InvokeScript%2A> and <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.ObjectForScripting%2A>, and <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Document%2A>.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="43542-108"><xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser> è soggetto ai vincoli di sicurezza del [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_wpf](~/includes/tla2sharptla-wpf-md.md)] applicazione che ospita il <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser>:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="43542-108"><xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser> is bound by the security constraints of the [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_wpf](~/includes/tla2sharptla-wpf-md.md)] application that is hosting the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser>:</span></span>  
  
-   <span data-ttu-id="43542-109">Quando <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser> è ospitato da un oggetto attendibilità [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_wpf](~/includes/tla2sharptla-wpf-md.md)] applicazione (un'applicazione autonoma, ad esempio), <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser> può ospitare [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_html](~/includes/tla2sharptla-html-md.md)] documenti da qualsiasi posizione.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="43542-109">When <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser> is hosted by a full-trust [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_wpf](~/includes/tla2sharptla-wpf-md.md)] application (a stand-alone application, for example), <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser> can host [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_html](~/includes/tla2sharptla-html-md.md)] documents from any location.</span></span>  
  
-   <span data-ttu-id="43542-110">Quando <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser> è ospitato da una relazione di trust parziale [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_wpf](~/includes/tla2sharptla-wpf-md.md)] applicazione (un [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_xbap](~/includes/tla2sharptla-xbap-md.md)], ad esempio), <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser> può ospitare solo i documenti **del sito di origine** file di dati dell'applicazione.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="43542-110">When <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser> is hosted by a partial-trust [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_wpf](~/includes/tla2sharptla-wpf-md.md)] application (an [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_xbap](~/includes/tla2sharptla-xbap-md.md)], for example), <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser> can only host documents that are **Site Of Origin** application data files.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="43542-111">Per altre informazioni, vedere [File di dati e di risorse dell'applicazione WPF](~/docs/framework/wpf/app-development/wpf-application-resource-content-and-data-files.md).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="43542-111">For more information, see [WPF Application Resource, Content, and Data Files](~/docs/framework/wpf/app-development/wpf-application-resource-content-and-data-files.md).</span></span>  
  
