## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="43542-161">Nell'esempio seguente viene illustrato come chiamare una funzione di script in un documento da un [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_wpf](~/includes/tla2sharptla-wpf-md.md)] applicazione utilizzando <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.InvokeScript%28System.String%29>.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="43542-161">The following example shows how to call a script function in a document from a [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_wpf](~/includes/tla2sharptla-wpf-md.md)] application by using <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.InvokeScript%28System.String%29>.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="43542-162">In questo esempio, la funzione di script non ha parametri.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="43542-162">In this example, the script function has no parameters.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="43542-163">Di seguito è riportato il [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_html](~/includes/tla2sharptla-html-md.md)] documento che implementa la funzione di script che verrà chiamata dal [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_wpf](~/includes/tla2sharptla-wpf-md.md)].</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="43542-163">The following is the [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_html](~/includes/tla2sharptla-html-md.md)] document that implements the script function that will be called from [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_wpf](~/includes/tla2sharptla-wpf-md.md)].</span></span>  
  
```html  
<html>  
    <head>  
        <script type="text/javascript">  
            // Function Without Parameters  
            function JavaScriptFunctionWithoutParameters()    
            {  
              outputID.innerHTML = "JavaScript function called!";  
            }  
        </script>  
    </head>  
    <body>  
    <div id="outputID" style="color:Red; font-size:16">  
        Hello from HTML document with script!  
    </div>  
    </body>  
</html>  
```  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="43542-164">Nella seguente il [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_wpf](~/includes/tla2sharptla-wpf-md.md)] implementazione per chiamare la funzione di script nel [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_html](~/includes/tla2sharptla-html-md.md)] documento.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="43542-164">The following shows the [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_wpf](~/includes/tla2sharptla-wpf-md.md)] implementation to call the script function in the [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_html](~/includes/tla2sharptla-html-md.md)] document.</span></span>  
  
```csharp  
private void callScriptFunctionNoParamButton_Click(object sender, RoutedEventArgs e)  
{  
  // Make sure the HTML document has loaded before attempting to  
  // invoke script of the document page. You could set loadCompleted  
  // to true when the LoadCompleted event on the WebBrowser fires.  
  if (this.loadCompleted)  
  {  
    try  
    {  
      this.webBrowser.InvokeScript("JavaScriptFunctionWithoutParameters");  
    }  
    catch (Exception ex)  
    {  
      string msg = "Could not call script: " +  
                   ex.Message +  
                  "\n\nPlease click the 'Load HTML Document with Script' button to load.";  
      MessageBox.Show(msg);  
    }  
  }  
}  
```

  
  
## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="43542-172"><xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.InvokeScript%28System.String%2CSystem.Object%5B%5D%29> non deve essere chiamato prima che il documento che implementa il completamento del caricamento.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="43542-172"><xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.InvokeScript%28System.String%2CSystem.Object%5B%5D%29> should not be called before the document that implements it has finished loading.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="43542-173">È possibile rilevare quando un documento ha terminato il caricamento mediante la gestione di <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.LoadCompleted> evento.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="43542-173">You can detect when a document has finished loading by handling the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.LoadCompleted> event.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="43542-174">Se non si passano valori di parametro sufficienti allo script che si sta chiamando, i parametri che non si passano valori avranno il valore non definito.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="43542-174">If you do not pass enough parameter values to the script that you are invoking, the parameters that you do not pass values to will have the undefined value.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="43542-175">Se si passano troppi valori di parametro, i valori in eccesso vengono ignorati.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="43542-175">If you pass too many parameter values, the excess values are ignored.</span></span>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="43542-176">Nell'esempio seguente viene illustrato come chiamare funzioni di script in un documento da un'applicazione utilizzando <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.InvokeScript%28System.String%2CSystem.Object%5B%5D%29>.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="43542-176">The following example shows how to call script functions in a document from an application by using <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.InvokeScript%28System.String%2CSystem.Object%5B%5D%29>.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="43542-177">In questo esempio, le funzioni di script richiedono parametri.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="43542-177">In this example, the script functions require parameters.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="43542-178">Di seguito è riportato il documento che implementa le funzioni di script che verranno chiamate dal [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_wpf](~/includes/tla2sharptla-wpf-md.md)].</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="43542-178">The following is the document that implements the script functions that will be called from [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_wpf](~/includes/tla2sharptla-wpf-md.md)].</span></span>  
  
```html  
<html>  
    <head>  
        <script type="text/javascript">  
            // Function Without Parameters  
            function JavaScriptFunctionWithoutParameters()    
            {  
              outputID.innerHTML = "JavaScript function 'called: " + message + ".";  
            }  
        </script>  
    </head>  
    <body>  
    <div id="outputID" style="color:Red; font-size:16">  
        Hello from HTML document with script!  
    </div>  
    </body>  
</html>  
```  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="43542-179">Nella seguente il [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_wpf](~/includes/tla2sharptla-wpf-md.md)] implementazione per chiamare lo script delle funzioni di [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_html](~/includes/tla2sharptla-html-md.md)] documento.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="43542-179">The following shows the [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_wpf](~/includes/tla2sharptla-wpf-md.md)] implementation to call the script functions in the [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_html](~/includes/tla2sharptla-html-md.md)] document.</span></span>  
  
```csharp  
private void callScriptFunctionNoParamButton_Click(object sender, RoutedEventArgs e)  
{  
  // Make sure the HTML document has loaded before attempting to  
  // invoke script of the document page. You could set loadCompleted  
  // to true when the LoadCompleted event on the WebBrowser fires.  
  if (this.loadCompleted)  
  {  
    try  
    {  
      this.webBrowser.InvokeScript("JavaScriptFunctionWithoutParameters", this.messageTextBox.Text);  
    }  
    catch (Exception ex)  
    {  
      string msg = "Could not call script: " +  
                   ex.Message +  
                  "\n\nPlease click the 'Load HTML Document with Script' button to load.";  
      MessageBox.Show(msg);  
    }  
  }  
}  
```

  
  
## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="43542-193">La chiamata <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Navigate%28System.Uri%29> ha lo stesso effetto dell'impostazione di <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Source%2A> proprietà.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="43542-193">Calling <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Navigate%28System.Uri%29> has the same effect as setting the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Source%2A> property.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="43542-194"><xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Source%2A> viene utilizzato dal markup dagli sviluppatori che desiderano specificare in modo dichiarativo il documento iniziale che <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser> passa quando <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser> viene inizializzato.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="43542-194"><xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Source%2A> is used from markup by developers who want to declaratively specify the initial document that <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser> navigates to when <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser> is initialized.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="43542-195">Utilizzare il <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Navigate%28System.String%29> metodo per passare a un URL che può includere caratteri di escape.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="43542-195">Use the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Navigate%28System.String%29> method to navigate to a URL that may include escape characters.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="43542-196">Utilizzare il <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Navigate%28System.Uri%29> metodo per passare a un <xref:System.Uri> che non includa caratteri di escape.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="43542-196">Use the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Navigate%28System.Uri%29> method to navigate to a <xref:System.Uri> that does not include escape characters.</span></span>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="43542-197">Nell'esempio seguente viene illustrato come utilizzare <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser> per passare a un documento usando il <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Navigate%28System.Uri%29> metodo.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="43542-197">The following example shows how to use <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser> to navigate to a document by using the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Navigate%28System.Uri%29> method.</span></span>  
  
```xaml  
<StackPanel>  
    <StackPanel Orientation="Horizontal">  
        <TextBox x:Name="addressTextBox" Width="200" />  
        <Button Click="goNavigateButton_Click">Go</Button>  
    </StackPanel>  
    <WebBrowser x:Name="myWebBrowser" />  
</StackPanel>  
```  
  
```csharp  
private void goNavigateButton_Click(object sender, RoutedEventArgs e)  
{  
    // Get URI to navigate to  
    Uri uri = new Uri(this.addressTextBox.Text, UriKind.RelativeOrAbsolute);  
  
    // Only absolute URIs can be navigated to  
    if (!uri.IsAbsoluteUri)  
    {  
        MessageBox.Show("The Address URI must be absolute eg 'http://www.microsoft.com'");  
        return;  
    }  
  
    // Navigate to the desired URL by calling the .Navigate method  
    this.myWebBrowser.Navigate(uri);  
}  
```

  
  
